    "Hadn't God shown mercy last time?",
    "Wouldn't He forgive them again?",
    "Despite his reservations, the Ninevites responded differently this time.",
    "With renewed urgency, they pleaded for mercy and begged Jonah to intercede on their behalf.",
    "They longed for a chance to prove themselves worthy of reprieve, hoping to avoid the coming judgment."
